<h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Best practices</h3>

<table class="govuk-table">
  <thead class="govuk-table__head">
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Do</th>
      <th scope="col" class="govuk-table__header">Don't</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody class="govuk-table__body">
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Review AI-generated alt-text for accuracy</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Accept alt-text without checking</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Add context the AI might miss (names, locations)</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Leave generic descriptions when specific ones help</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Keep alt-text concise and meaningful</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Start with "Image of..." or "Photo of..."</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Use empty alt="" for purely decorative images</td>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">Add alt-text to decorative images</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<div class="govuk-warning-text">
  <span class="govuk-warning-text__icon" aria-hidden="true">!</span>
